snippet.title: Alkaline Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Alkaline: an enhanced Base mod/map pack for Quake.
Official website: https://alkalinequake.wordpress.com/
UPDATED 1.1 version! Out now: https://www.quaddicted.com/filebase/alkaline1.1.zip
Classic 1.0: https://www.quaddicted.com/filebase/alkaline.zip

The accompanying map pack includes maps from Bal, Bloodshot,
bmFbr, Greenwood, Grome, Juzley, Makkon, Mista Heita, 
Scampie & Greenwood, and last, but definitely not the least, zigi.

Includes original music from AlekswithaK and Immorpher.
